data.description: Price Improvement.  Location, Location, Location!  Outstanding, immaculate Palm II located in popular Del Webb Spruce Creek Golf & CC on #8 of the Masters golf course. Picture perfect views!  Located on a cul-de-sac near front entrance.  Convenient to the golf course, Horizon center, main pool and the Liberty Grill.  Living room & dining room with cathedral ceilings.  Spacious dine-in kitchen, above cabinet lighting, bay window & plantation shutters.  Laminate flooring in living room, dining room & kitchen.  Office with built-ins & pocket door off kitchen.  Carpeting in bedrooms. Tiled bathrooms with granite counters.  Home has a  24' x 12' tiled Florida room & an enclosed lanai, both under air & heat.  The backyard has an open patio with a fenced area.  Everything needed to enjoy the beautiful views of the golf course and the fall weather.  Extra long driveway to garage with sliding screens, acrylic floor, utility sink, washer, dryer, & pull down stairs with attic storage.  Your own irrigation well saves on watering bills.  ADT security system, is not activated. Roof 2014, HVAC 2013, water heater 3/2023.  Assumable VA loan at 2.75%.  Dining room fixture & draperies in both bedrooms do not convey.
